<br>
This is my first post as a Merc.. I've been solely Hib since release, but am trying the Merc as my first Alb character. Right up front I'll say that I love it!<br>
<br>
My question is this: does DW work the same as Hib CD or is it sort of a cross between CD and LA? <br>
<br>
From my understanding, CD works like so: each round the game checks your CD to see if you swing both. Whether you swing both or not, it then randoms which delay to use for the swing. Both weapons use your full wepskill to determine damage. This makes having two nearly identical weapons the best route to take.<br>
<br>
For LA: you swing both weps always, with damage on the mainhand at full wepskill and LA damage at wepskill modified by LA skill. Your delay is just an average of your two weapons, so generally having one very slow wep and one fast wep is best.<br>
<br>
How does DW fit in there? Am I off on how I think CD works? Can someone set me straight? My whole purpose in asking this is to find out if I should be looking at similar or different delay weps for RvR.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance,<br>
<br>
Cheers,<br>
