<br>
But the delay isn't randomized... It's the 'average' of the two weapons you are using if you hit with both...<br>
<br>
And the best route, with high DW, is arguably having a slow, powerful right hand weapon and a real quick left hand weapon... So that when you hit with both (Which should happen fairly often) it will be the average of those weapons<br>
<br>
But some prefer two of the same speed weapons, the speed is more reliable then but the damage suffers some... It's really all personal preference... But me, I use a 3.6 speed right hand and a 2.4 left hand... <p>Vith<br>
